    "rationale": "This is a classic and simple example of the Hofmann-L\u00f6ffler-Freytag reaction. The substrate, N-chloro-N-methylbutan-1-amine, undergoes a 1,5-hydrogen atom transfer upon treatment with acid (e.g., sulfuric acid) and light/heat to form a \u03b4-chloroamine intermediate, which then cyclizes to form the pyrrolidinium salt. Subsequent basic workup (implied) yields the final product, 1-methylpyrrolidine. This example clearly demonstrates the key features: an N-haloamine substrate, intramolecular C-H activation at a remote (\u03b4) position, and subsequent cyclization to form a five-membered ring.",
